node.text: Hey Rich People! So- to kick off Personal Finance Week on #MDJSTIMULUS I obvi want to talk about UR MONEY. Specifically, ur $ during COVID. People are struggling financially rn + the gov is trying to help them (like Chris Harrison does when the bachelor is having trouble... 🌹) That’s what the stimulus package is!!!! Oh, and for the sake of transparency- there’s been 3 financial relief packages passed so far. But this vid is about the THIRD. Why not the first two? Well they don’t really effect UR MONEY + it’s ~*Personal Finance Week*~ after all #MDJStimulus. The 3rd is the largest stimulus package in history ($2T) and includes the $1200 stimulus check- which I know u have been wondering about. Also, COMMENT any questions you have! And let me know if ur stim checks come! They’re supposed to be mailed today. The government LOVESS 4/20 🚬 🌱 . #PersonalFinanceWeek #MDJStimulus #FinanceIsCool

node.text: I think cutting someone’s salary is beyond rude. Like ok, we literally agreed on a set amount and now you’re reducing it. I know we are in a down economy but a deals a deal! How dare you, Shira. But i also think being a rich, successful person is a state of mind. So even though getting a salary cut is less than ideal, j'cannot let it drag you down. Instead, view it as a wakeup call. Speaking of which-  welcome to my new series: Wakeup Call with Mrs. Dow Jones. Let me know what you think in the comments :) P.S. It's Day 3 of JOB WEEK and wow, time flies when you're talking about employment. How are you liking #MDJStimulus? Feedback so appreciated!! (Art by @bethany_richard per usual- she’s the Picasso of our time)

node.title: MY BOSS CUT MY SALARY!! | Mrs. Dow Jones

node.text:
It's day two of ~JOB WEEK~ so we obvi have to talk about HOW TO GET A NEW JOB!

With unemployment rates at a high and companies cutting positions left and right, it doesn't feel like the best time to be looking. But you know what- it never is! Like when has it ever been easy to get a job. Nope, never. Ok, maybe that ONE time that my Dad hired me to clean his car but usually, it's an uphill climb. So stay the course! Be patient! And use the 8-tips from this video. They are tried and true and gonna help.

Also- I refer to us as being in a "recession" during this video. I want this video to be relevant for you during this full crisis- past Quarantine- and Jamie Dimon- the last standing big-bank CEO after the 2008 financial crisis- said that "a bad recession is coming". So, that's why I said it. It hasn't been officially declared yet but when ya know ya know! Anyways, comment below with your thoughts or what color your manicure is or just share a secret. P.S. How are you liking #MDJStimulus so far?  #financeiscool (cover art by the insanely talented @bethany_richard)

node.text: Are luxury watches a good investment? I wanted to investigate, so I met up with Brynn from @dimepiece.co and we talked to the EXPERT @kelly_yoch from @watchesofswitzerland_us! People go broke trying to look rich! Not in this house hehe. #financeiscool #paidpartnership
